###EXPLORE THE FLASK MODULE AND CREATE A WEB SERVER USING FLASK & PYTHON..

📦 1. Install Flask
pip install flask

🗂️ 2. Create Project Structure
flask_app/
│
├── app.py
└── templates/
    └── index.html


🧠 3. Code for app.py (Your Flask Server)
from flask import Flask
app = Flask(__name__)

@app.route("/")
def hello_world():
    return "<p>Hello, World!</p>"

app.run()

▶️ 5. Run the Server
